casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Nance, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Nance, 114 Ohio St.3d 122, 2007-Ohio-3654.]

(No. 2006-1018 Submitted July 10, 2007 Decided August 1, 2007.)

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is reversed on the authority of State v. Williams, 114 Ohio St.3d 103, 2007-Ohio-3268, 868 N.E.2d 969.

Moyer, C.J., Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. Cupp, J., not participating. *123F. Stephen Chamberlain, for appellant.
